    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1640971103311-x200.jpg",
