            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to the pan with a couple of splashes of <strong>water</strong> and cook, covered for a further 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
