    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s] </strong>lengthways until you have thin strips</p><p>Slice your <strong>cucumber[s]</strong> into discs</p><p>Slice each individual <strong>cucumber disc </strong>into matchsticks</p>",
