    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is done, shred it apart in the pan, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Mix the <strong>pulled</strong> <strong>chicken </strong>into the pan juices</p>",
      "order": 7,
